This error is from running the CI script, which builds a ubuntu based docker container, so I think gcc is correct in that case? 

I'm following the instructions on the [contributing info page](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md), to run unit tests for PRs I'm making. Really I just want to run cpu unit tests, and I ran into this issue on the way.
